{"word":"Α","slug":"Α","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>Α, α, τό</el></b> first letter of the Greek alphabet, <b><i>alpha,</i></b> <el>αʹ</el> as numeral = <i>one</i> or <i>first,</i> in titles of <b>1 Cor</b> <i>etc.</i> See also <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἄλφα\">ἄλφα</a></el>. <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:Ἀαρών\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}